org.hps.record.daqconfig2019

Class DAQConfig2019

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.daqconfig2019.IDAQConfig2019
      • org.hps.record.daqconfig2019.DAQConfig2019

  • public class DAQConfig2019
extends IDAQConfig2019
    Class DAQConfig2019 holds all of the supported parameters from the DAQ configuration that exists in EVIO files. These values are stored in various subclasses appropriate to the parameter that are accessed through this primary interface.
